### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Welcome
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/welcome

###

### --- Repair Orders ---

### List all repair orders (defaults)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders

### List all repair orders (custom pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders?page=0&size=100&sort=status&direction=asc

### Get repair order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders/01966c3a-1000-7000-8000-000000000001

### Create repair order with line items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Brake inspection and replacement",
  "vehicleMake": "Toyota",
  "vehicleModel": "Corolla",
  "vehicleYear": 2022,
  "licensePlate": "TEST-001",
  "customerId": "01966c3a-0000-7000-8000-000000000001",
  "lineItems": [
    {
      "description": "Front brake pads",
      "unitPrice": 89.99
    },
    {
      "description": "Labor - brake service (1 hr)",
      "unitPrice": 75.00
    }
  ]
}

### Create repair order without line items
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Quick vehicle inspection",
  "vehicleMake": "Honda",
  "vehicleModel": "Civic",
  "vehicleYear": 2024,
  "customerId": "01966c3a-0000-7000-8000-000000000002"
}

### Update repair order (replace <id> and version)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders/01966c3a-1000-7000-8000-000000000003
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: 1

{
  "description": "Engine diagnostic — completed",
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "vehicleMake": "Ford",
  "vehicleModel": "F-150",
  "vehicleYear": 2023,
  "licensePlate": "DEF-9012"
}

### Delete repair order
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders/01966c3a-1000-7000-8000-000000000004

###

### --- Error scenarios ---

### Get non-existing repair order (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Create with non-existing customer (404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Should fail",
  "vehicleMake": "Toyota",
  "vehicleModel": "Camry",
  "vehicleYear": 2021,
  "licensePlate": "SWU-849",
  "customerId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### Create with invalid body (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": ""
}

### Update with wrong version (412)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/repair-orders/01966c3a-1000-7000-8000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: 999

{
  "description": "Should fail",
  "status": "COMPLETED",
  "vehicleMake": "Toyota",
  "vehicleModel": "Camry",
  "vehicleYear": 2021
}
